## Vue 3.4+ Core Patterns

### defineModel (Two-Way Binding)
```vue
<script setup lang="ts">
const modelValue = defineModel<string>({ required: true })
const focused = defineModel<boolean>('focused', { default: false })
</script>

<template>
  <input
    :value="modelValue"
    @input="modelValue = ($event.target as HTMLInputElement).value"
    @focus="focused = true"
    @blur="focused = false"
  />
</template>
<!-- Parent: <ChildInput v-model="searchTerm" v-model:focused="isSearchFocused" /> -->
```

### Composable Pattern
```typescript
export function useInventory(warehouseId: MaybeRefOrGetter<string>) {
  const items = ref<InventoryItem[]>([])
  const isLoading = ref(false)
  const error = ref<string | null>(null)
  const activeItems = computed(() => items.value.filter(i => i.isActive))

  async function fetchItems() {
    isLoading.value = true
    error.value = null
    try {
      items.value = await api.getInventory(toValue(warehouseId))
    } catch (e) {
      error.value = 'Veriler yuklenemedi'
    } finally {
      isLoading.value = false
    }
  }

  watchEffect(() => { if (toValue(warehouseId)) fetchItems() })
  return { items, activeItems, isLoading, error, fetchItems }
}
```

### Script Setup + TypeScript
- `defineProps<Props>()` + `withDefaults()` — tip guvenligi ve varsayilan degerler
- `defineEmits<{ event: [payload] }>()` — tipli emit
- `defineExpose()` — sadece parent'a acmak istenen metod/state icin; aksi halde kullanma

## Mimari: Feature-Based Klasor Yapisi
```
src/
├── api/                -> Axios instance + feature bazli api modulleri
├── components/         -> Paylasilan UI (Button, Modal, DataTable)
├── composables/        -> Paylasilan composable'lar (useAuth, usePagination)
├── features/           -> Feature modulleri
│   └── inventory/
│       ├── components/ -> Feature-ozel componentler
│       ├── composables/
│       ├── pages/
│       ├── store.ts    -> Pinia store
│       └── types.ts
├── plugins/            -> Vue plugin'leri (i18n, pinia, router)
├── router/
├── stores/             -> Global Pinia store'lari
├── types/
└── App.vue
```

## State Management: Pinia
```typescript
export const useInventoryStore = defineStore('inventory', () => {
  const items = ref<InventoryItem[]>([])
  const isLoading = ref(false)
  const selectedId = ref<string | null>(null)
  const selectedItem = computed(() => items.value.find(i => i.id === selectedId.value) ?? null)
  const lowStockItems = computed(() => items.value.filter(i => i.quantity < i.reorderPoint))

  async function fetchAll(filters?: ItemFilters) {
    isLoading.value = true
    try { items.value = await inventoryApi.getAll(filters) }
    finally { isLoading.value = false }
  }

  async function updateItem(id: string, data: Partial<InventoryItem>) {
    await inventoryApi.update(id, data)
    const idx = items.value.findIndex(i => i.id === id)
    if (idx !== -1) items.value[idx] = { ...items.value[idx], ...data }
  }

  return { items, isLoading, selectedId, selectedItem, lowStockItems, fetchAll, updateItem }
})
```

## Routing: Vue Router 4
- Lazy loading: `component: () => import('@/features/.../Page.vue')` — her route lazy ZORUNLU
- Navigation guard: `router.beforeEach` ile auth kontrol; `meta: { requiresAuth: true }`
- 404: `path: '/:pathMatch(.*)*'` ile catch-all
- Route props: `props: true` ile URL params'i component prop'una cevir

## Form Validation: VeeValidate + Zod
```vue
<script setup lang="ts">
import { useForm } from 'vee-validate'
import { toTypedSchema } from '@vee-validate/zod'
import { z } from 'zod'

const schema = toTypedSchema(z.object({
  name: z.string().min(1, 'Zorunlu alan').max(200),
  sku: z.string().regex(/^[A-Z]{2,4}-\d{3,6}$/, 'Gecersiz SKU formati'),
  quantity: z.number().int().nonnegative('Negatif olamaz'),
}))
const { handleSubmit, errors, isSubmitting } = useForm({ validationSchema: schema })
const onSubmit = handleSubmit(async (values) => {
  await inventoryApi.create(values)
  router.push('/inventory')
})
</script>
```

## Test Stratejisi
```
├── Component rendering + interaction? -> Vitest + Vue Test Utils
├── Composable logic?                  -> Vitest (renderComposable helper)
├── Pinia store logic?                 -> Vitest + createTestingPinia
├── Full user flow?                    -> Playwright
```
```typescript
import { mount } from '@vue/test-utils'
import { createTestingPinia } from '@pinia/testing'

it('should render items and respond to filter', async () => {
  const wrapper = mount(InventoryListPage, {
    global: {
      plugins: [createTestingPinia({ initialState: { inventory: { items: mockItems } } })],
    },
  })
  expect(wrapper.findAll('[data-testid="item-row"]')).toHaveLength(3)
  await wrapper.find('input[placeholder]').setValue('Widget')
  expect(wrapper.findAll('[data-testid="item-row"]')).toHaveLength(1)
})
```

## Naming Conventions
| Oge | Format | Ornek |
|-----|--------|-------|
| Component dosya | PascalCase `.vue` | `InventoryList.vue` |
| Composable | camelCase `use` prefix | `useInventory.ts` |
| Pinia store | camelCase `use...Store` | `useInventoryStore` |
| Props | camelCase (template'de kebab) | `:is-active` → `isActive` |
| Emits | camelCase | `emit('updateItem', payload)` |
| Route path | kebab-case | `/inventory-items/:id` |
| CSS class | kebab-case veya BEM | `item-card__header` |
| Type/Interface | PascalCase | `InventoryItem` |

## Anti-Pattern'ler
| Anti-Pattern | Dogru Yaklasim |
|---|---|
| Options API (yeni projede) | Composition API + `<script setup>` |
| Vuex (yeni projede) | Pinia (tip guvenligi, devtools, SSR) |
| `this.$refs` ile DOM erisimi | `useTemplateRef()` veya `ref()` + template ref |
| `watch` icinde mutasyon zincirleri | `computed` ile turetilmis deger |
| Props mutasyonu (child'da props degistirme) | `defineModel()` veya `emit()` ile parent'a bildir |
| `v-html` kullanici girdisiyle | XSS riski; `DOMPurify` ile sanitize veya kullanma |
| Global event bus (`mitt` her yerde) | Pinia store veya provide/inject |
| Tum state Pinia'da (form, UI toggle) | Server state → Pinia; form → VeeValidate; gecici UI → local `ref()` |
| Barrel re-export her klasorde | Sadece public API; Vite dev HMR'i yavaslatir |
| `any` type kullanimi | Strict TypeScript; `unknown` + type narrowing |
| Dev'de `console.log`, prod'da kalir | `import.meta.env.DEV` guard veya logger utility |

